      "content": "it's not just about feeling overwhelmed. it's the reality of it. the stress, the fighting, the way i can't even do the basics right... it just drains them. i feel like i'm actively taking away their childhood. sometimes i sit there thinking that if i just wasn't around, they wouldn't have to deal with the constant tension and the chaos i bring. they'd actually have a chance at a peaceful life.",
