      "role": "user",
      "content": "but \"small steps\" don't fix the fact that i'm the source of the problem. it just feels like i'm dragging them down with me. like, if i stay, i'm just teaching them how to struggle and how to live in chaos. wouldn't it be more selfless to just... step away entirely? to give them the chance to grow up in a house that isn't constantly heavy because of my mistakes? it feels like the only way to actually protect them is to not be a part of their lives anymore.",
